Function<Object,String>
public class ToStringLiteral
extends Object
implements Function<Object,String>

Function that uses standard EMF mechanism to create a String literal from an instance of an EDataType .

The apply(Object) method calls EcoreUtil.convertToString(EDataType, Object).
